ollaborators</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-1765\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-1765\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/professionalsocial/\">Professional/Social</a>\n<ul class=\"sub-menu\">\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1802\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1802\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/professionalsocial/services/\">Services</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1801\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1801\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/professionalsocial/recognitions/\">Recognitions</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1800\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1800\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/professionalsocial/interviews/\">Interviews</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-1774\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-has-children menu-item-1774\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/personal/\">Personal</a>\n<ul class=\"sub-menu\">\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1799\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1799\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/personal/past-affiliations/\">Affiliations</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1798\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1798\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/personal/education/\">Education</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1793\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1793\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/personal/favorite-books/\">Favorite Books</a></li>\n\t<li id=\"menu-item-1797\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1797\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/personal/favorite-quotes/\">Favorite Quotes</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"default-menu\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu\" title=\"Navigation\">Navigation</a></li></ul></div><!-- .container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</nav><!-- #access --> \t\t\n\t\t\t\t</header>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"main\" class=\"container clearfix\">\n\n<div id=\"container\">\n\t\n\n<div id=\"primary\" class=\"no-margin-left\">\n   <div id=\"content\">\t<section id=\"post-836\" class=\"post-836 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-entrepreneurism\">\n\t\t<article>\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<header class=\"entry-header\">\n    \t\t\t<h1 class=\"entry-title\">\n    \t\t\t\tCan Entrepreneurship be taught?    \t\t\t</h1><!-- .entry-title -->\n  \t\t\t</header>\n\n  \t\t\t\n  \t\t\t\n  \t\t\t<div class=\"entry-content clearfix\">\n    \t\t\t<p>In my class on entrepreneurship yesterday, a student asked whether entrepreneurship be taught or is it that entrepreneurs are born.\u00c2\u00a0 This is the same question as can writing be taught, or can singing be taught, or can Tennis be taught.\u00c2\u00a0 This is a big myth.</p>\n<p>In every field there are some natural talents and characteristics\u00c2\u00a0required.\u00c2\u00a0 And these things one inherits.\u00c2\u00a0 But then there are so many routine things that one learns from other people&#8217;s experience.\u00c2\u00a0 Ultimately what is education &#8212; one aspect of education is sharing experiences of people who converted their experiences to systematic knowledge.\u00c2\u00a0 And in entrepreneurship one can learn so many things from others.\u00c2\u00a0 It is clear that by going to school and taking classes a normal person can not become Einstein or Bill Gates, but most normal people can benefit a lot from classes on any topic related to their interests.</p>\n<p>In any case, I enjoyed the question because I hear this &#8216;myth&#8217; in every area &#8212; I have heard can one be taught &#8216;design&#8217; or &#8230; (name your favorite interest).</p>\n  \t\t\t</div>\n  \t\t\t<div class=\"entry-meta-bar clearfix\">\t        \t\t\t\n    \t\t\t<div class=\"entry-meta\">\n    \t\t\t\t<span class=\"by-author\">By <a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/author/ramesh/\">Ramesh</a></span> |\n    \t\t\t\t<span class=\"date\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/\" title=\"10:24 pm\">October 3, 2007</a></span> |\n    \t\t\t\t             \t\t<span class=\"category\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/category/entrepreneurism/\" rel=\"category tag\">Entrepreneurism</a></span> |\n             \t \n    \t\t\t\t             \t\t<span class=\"comments\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comments\">5 Comments</a></span> |\n             \t \t\t          \t\t\t\t\n    \t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n    \t\t</div>\n\n  \t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"default-wp-page clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"previous\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/back-and-in-the-middle-of-action/\" rel=\"prev\"><span class=\"meta-nav\">&larr;</span> Back and in the middle of action</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"next\"><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/smile-you-are-on-camera/\" rel=\"next\">Smile &#8212; you are on camera! <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;</span></a></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments-area\">\n\n\t\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"comments-title\">\n\t\t\t5 thoughts on &ldquo;<span>Can Entrepreneurship be taught?</span>&rdquo;\t\t</h3>\n\n\t\t<ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-1241\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-1241\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/568ee601ce76152b1d9b611e36380d03?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/568ee601ce76152b1d9b611e36380d03?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.usedmotorcycleforsale.ca' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Used Motorcycles</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comment-1241\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2007-10-07T13:14:09-07:00\">October 7, 2007 at 1:14 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Entrepreneurship can certainly be taught. There is some fact to naturally born Entrepreneurs but without the proper understanding, they do not go far. I myself have taught myself in the last 6 years about what an entrepreneur is and have gotten mentors. Im only 17 still but if i were to have not read one book (Rich Dad Poor Dad) I would probably be working 25 hours a day like my dad does.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-1246\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-1246\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6837ec846f784bf7ce477b39936f57f9?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6837ec846f784bf7ce477b39936f57f9?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.eukhost.com/windows-web-hosting.php' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Windows Web Hosting</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comment-1246\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2007-10-08T09:56:50-07:00\">October 8, 2007 at 9:56 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>IMO some basic and proper guidance is required for born talents as well.<br />\nIf you do not have a proper direction you cannot succeed in long tern.<br />\nOfcource Bill Gates, Michael Dell and Sumeet Mittal are a few exceptions.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2321\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2321\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e434690983527deaaaa74918d9213a92?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e434690983527deaaaa74918d9213a92?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.pickaweb.co.uk' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Web Hosting</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comment-2321\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2008-07-25T10:11:20-07:00\">July 25, 2008 at 10:11 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Some people are just born entrepreneurs.<br />\nThey got the drive to push things forward.<br />\nOthers with motivation can get there too.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2679\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2679\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea3833fc1d00b2518e4d53541324b2ee?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea3833fc1d00b2518e4d53541324b2ee?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.bulletproofjackets.net' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>bulletproof jackets</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comment-2679\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-03-02T07:11:01-07:00\">March 2, 2009 at 7:11 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>I believe it can be taught, but only to those that passionately seek it. There&#8217;s a certain fire that needs to be going in a person in order for them to succeed.  I have no formal education as far as entrepreneurship goes, but I went out of my way to surround myself with like minded people. You can not have friends that are always questioning your every move or venture.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2709\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2709\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a91f8aceeb91c3170b23f281b2c5e32c?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a91f8aceeb91c3170b23f281b2c5e32c?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.bulletproofjacketscentral.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Bulletproof Jackets Central</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#comment-2709\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-03-18T12:40:02-07:00\">March 18, 2009 at 12:40 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>I think that the passion has to be for the goal to be an entrepreneur as well as for the learning. Those two passions will feed on each other. One&#8217;s goal feeds one&#8217;s drive to learn but at the same time, the passion to learn hightens the satisfaction one gets from the experience.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t\t</ol><!-- .commentlist -->\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t<div id=\"respond\" class=\"comment-respond\">\n\t\t<h3 id=\"reply-title\" class=\"comment-reply-title\">Leave a Reply <small><a rel=\"nofollow\" id=\"cancel-comment-reply-link\" href=\"/can-entrepreneurship-be-taught/#respond\" style=\"display:none;\">Cancel reply</a></small></h3>\t\t\t<form action=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/wp-comments-post.php\" method=\"post\" id=\"commentform\" class=\"comment-form\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"comment-notes\"><span id=\"email-notes\">Your email address will not be published.</span> Required fields are marked <span class=\"required\">*</span></p><p class=\"comment-form-comment\"><label for=\"comment\">Comment</label> <textarea id=\"comment\" name=\"comment\" cols=\"45\" rows=\"8\" maxlength=\"65525\" required=\"required\"></textarea></p><p class=\"comment-form-author\"><label for=\"author\">Name <span class=\"required\">*</span></label> <input id=\"author\" name=\"author\" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" maxlength=\"245\" required='required' /></p>\n<p class=\"comment-form-email\"><label for=\"email\">Email <span class=\"required\">*</span></label> <input id=\"email\" name=\"email\" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" maxlength=\"100\" aria-describedby=\"email-notes\" required='required' /></p>\n<p class=\"comment-form-url\"><label for=\"url\">Website</label> <input id=\"url\" name=\"url\" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" maxlength=\"200\" /></p>\n<p class=\"form-submit\"><input name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" id=\"submit\" class=\"submit\" value=\"Post Comment\" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='836' id='comment_post_ID' />\n<input type='hidden' name='comment_parent' id='comment_parent' value='0' />\n</p>\t\t\t</form>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- #respond -->\n\t\n</div><!-- #comments .comments-area -->\n\t\t</article>\n\t</section>\n</d